Key Match Events: Goalkeeper Dang Van Lam made three important saves in the first half and two more in the second half.
Iraq scored the winning goal in the last seconds of the match with Mohanad Ali's header.
Post-Match Reflections: Dang Van Lam expressed regret over the last-minute loss but emphasized the team's determination to correct mistakes and come back stronger.
Captain Que Ngoc Hai acknowledged the defeat but highlighted the positive aspects, such as the performance of young players and the team's overall effort.
